nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在装箱的时候自动调用的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Integer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">valueOf(int)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">方法。而在拆箱的时候自动调用的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Integer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">intValue</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">方法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>因此可以用一句话总结装箱和拆箱的实现过程：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>　　装箱过程是通过调用包装器的<span lang=\"EN-US\">valueOf</span>方法实现的，而拆箱过程是通过调用包装器的<span lang=\"EN-US\"> xxxValue</span>方法实现的。（<span lang=\"EN-US\">xxx</span>代表对应的基本数据类型）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">valueOf</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">方法创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Integer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">对象的时候，如果数值在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[-128,127]</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">之间，便返回指向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IntegerCache.cache</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">中已经存在的对象的引用；否则创建一个新的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Integer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">对象。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span>注意，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Integer</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Short</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Byte</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Character</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Long</span>这几个类的<span lang=\"EN-US\">valueOf</span>方法的实现是类似的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span>　　　　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">Double</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Float</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">valueOf</span>方法的实现是类似的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”==“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals()</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的区别？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>&nbsp; </span>==</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">比较两个变量是否相等，如果是基本数据类型，两个数值直接比较，如果是引用数据类型，比较的是两个对象的首地址</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的源码可以看出这里定义的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">==</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">是等效的（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Object</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">类中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">没什么区别），不同的原因就在于有些类（像</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">String</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Integer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">等类）对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">进行了重写，但是没有对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">进行重写的类（比如我们自己写的类）就只能从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Object</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">类中继承</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">方法，其</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">方法与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">==</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">就也是等效的，除非我们在此类中重写</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">equals</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:red\'=\"\" lang=\"EN-USCalibri&quot;,sans-serif;\">String</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:red\">类型比较不同对象内容是否相同，应该用</span></strong><strong><span mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:red\'=\"\" lang=\"EN-USCalibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\">equals</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:red\">，因为</span></strong><strong><span mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:red\'=\"\" lang=\"EN-USCalibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\">==</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:red\">用于比较引用类型和比较基本数据类型时具有不同的功能。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:46.35pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5、<spantimes new=\"\" roman\"\'=\"\">&nbsp;\r\n</spantimes></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:black;mso-themecolor:\r\ntext1\" lang=\"EN-US\">String</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font